@base = http://localhost:8000/api

### Get score personality label
GET {{base}}/analytics/personality

### Get monthly Wrapped (previous month by default)
GET {{base}}/analytics/wrapped

### Get monthly Wrapped for a specific month
GET {{base}}/analytics/wrapped?month=2026-03

### Get anonymous score percentile vs cohort
GET {{base}}/analytics/percentile

### Get score milestones (marks as celebrated)
GET {{base}}/analytics/milestones

### Get community stats (anonymized, this week)
GET {{base}}/analytics/community
